s/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927e4914fa24744c659b52969e49c1370f5d4151","tid":2213382,"uid":27568,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:13:43.000Z","msg":"うま塩 (旨鹽)<br />\n【うましお】 【umashio】<br />\n【名】<br />\n<br />\n〈食〉咸鲜（口味）。「塩味は単に塩で味付けしているだけで、うま塩は塩分以外にうまみ成分などが含まれている。」<br />\n<br />\n鹽唔係只有鹽的味道，旨鹽包含鹽分以外的鮮味(或美味)"},{"pid":"ee67eca7f2c1abdff4a8298a15f5ca974981d060","tid":2213382,"uid":27568,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"事實上，旨味有兩個意思。一個是單純表現美味的旨味。在日文中「旨い(UMAI)」就如同「美味しい(OISHII)」一樣，旨味對日本人來說，就是表現食物非常美味的一個說法。這個意思應該是指所有食材的使用都是沒有問題的。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，旨味即為甜、酸、鹹、苦，後的第五種味覺。是於1908年，由舊東京帝國大學(現 東京大學)的池田菊苗博士所發現的，屬於日本發明的味覺。<br />\n<br />\n指鮮味<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.japaholic.com/tw/article/28605/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.japaholic.com%2Ftw%2Farticle%2F28605%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I22g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=c43780b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.japaholic.com/tw/article/28605/</a>"},{"pid":"a3b7aab697986150171a733f230d1b232ab7cf03","tid":2213382,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"鹽味係只有鹽的味道，旨鹽就包含鹽分以外的鮮味(或美味)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞錯左"},{"pid":"2c52c62f025c2b7ac9ce34909398fe723f55c6d6","tid":2213382,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"旨宮頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77c6272bdbe0fbc1b287ebfa929e07bd65f1616","tid":2213382,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3b3c96ef872dfbd680f8f5409fc4233487a128fb","tid":2213382,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"定延煮嘅嘢=旨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img1.daumcd